  34. http://www.wxtide32.com/
  35. http://airtaxi.net/ctide/
  36. http://www.tj-eichler.de/muTide/
  37. http://www.tj-eichler.de/muTide/
  38. http://tech.groups.yahoo.com/group/timexdatalinkusb/
  39. http://tech.groups.yahoo.com/group/timexdatalinkusbdevelop/
  40. http://heygus.2y.net/hptide
  41. http://www.hpcalc.org/details.php?id=3943
  42. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/installation.html
