  90. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/xttpd.html
  91. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/installation.html#trouble
  92. mailto:dave@flaterco.com
  93. http://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/station_retrieve.shtml?type=Bench+Mark+Data+Sheets
  94. http://www.iana.org/time-zones
  95. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/sysreq.html#TZsysreq
  96. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/time_t.html
  97. http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golan_v._Holder
  98. http://www.debian.org/doc/debian-policy/ch-archive.html#s-dfsg
  99. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/harmonics.html#harmgen
