   7. http://windows.microsoft.com/en-US/windows7/Preview-the-appearance-of-a-printed-webpage
   8. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/BarHarbor.pdf
   9. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/mincurrents.html
  10. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/xtide1diff.html
  11. http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/xtide.html#contents
